GET	/api/market/items/{itemId}	获取指定二手商品的详细信息:
需要返回的格式：
{
  "itemId": "uuid-string",
  "title": "Used Laptop",
  "description": "Good condition...",
  "price": 500.00,
  "sellerId": "uuid-string",
  "sellerUsername": "john_doe",
  "sellerAvatarUrl": "http://...",
  "createdAt": "timestamp",
  "status": "available",
  "images": ["http://...", "http://..."],
  "category": "electronics",
  "views": 120,
  "location": "Building B"
}